data.description: Amazing opportunity to purchase this large property in the city of Wilmington. 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bathroom house thats completely renovated. New Wood Floors throughout, Stainless steal appliances, freshly painted walls, Granite Countertops and a huge storage shed that can fit a small car. 3 large bedrooms with ample closet space, 2 full bathrooms including 1 in the main bedroom, half bath on the first floor, central AC, and more. This home is just minutes to local shopping, schools, downtown attractions and I95. you can get to Philadelphia Airport in 15 minutes!!!!. The seller is a licensed Realtor.
